data.title: Christmas Tidings Card
data.meta_description: Everyone gets excited about holiday greetings this time of year. Even this gathering of forest friends in Dona Gelsinger's painting. Made in the USA.
data.text:
Everyone gets excited about holiday greetings this time of year. Even this gathering of forest friends in Dona Gelsinger's painting. Made in the USA. Exclusive.

Verse: Warmest thoughts and best wishes for a wonderful holiday and a very Happy New Year

Features:

Sold in boxes of 18 cards and 18 envelopes

7 7/8" x 5 5/8" folded

Recycled white envelope with red foil lining

Personalize your cards - just $9.00 for the first box and $2.50 for each additional box of the same design and imprint.

Return Address imprint on your envelopes - just $9.00 for the first box of envelopes and $2.50 for each additional box of the same design and imprint.
